<h5 id="subject_1114517">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=2609ca61d30f70e2865a0dde3abf860c&amp;topic=125460.msg1114517#msg1114517" rel="nofollow">Re: 【BotC】牧师变体：三元教士（Triadic Priest）</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1114517'));undefined;">繁</a>
